### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Task 1 — Create a transaction (transfer)
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Task 1 — Create a deposit
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-EXTRN",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 500,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Task 1 — List all transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions

### Task 1 — Get transaction by id
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/REPLACE_WITH_ID

### Task 1 — Get account balance
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### Task 2 — Invalid amount (negative)
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": -10,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Task 2 — Invalid currency
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 10,
  "currency": "XYZ",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Task 3 — Filter by accountId
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

### Task 3 — Filter by type
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?type=transfer

### Task 3 — Filter by date range
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?from=2025-01-01&to=2026-12-31

### Task 3 — Combined filters
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=transfer&from=2025-01-01

### Task 4A — Account summary
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-12345/summary

### Task 4B — Simple interest
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-12345/interest?rate=0.05&days=30

### Task 4C — CSV export
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/export?format=csv

### Task 4D — Rate limiting (надсилай швидко 100+ разів для перевірки 429)
GET http://localhost:3000/health
